<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Prologue — Meet Sadie | HoldOff</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Before you send that message, meet the part of you that already knows better.">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
      background: #0d0a14;
      color: #e8dcc8;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* ── ambient background ── */
    .bg-layer {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% -10%, rgba(120, 60, 180, 0.22) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 80% 100%, rgba(80, 30, 120, 0.18) 0%, transparent 65%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0d0a14 0%, #130d20 50%, #0d0a14 100%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* ── layout ── */
    .prologue-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 60px 28px 80px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    /* ── chapter label ── */
    .chapter-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.55);
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.3s;
    }

    /* ── scenes ── */
    .scene {
      width: 100%;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .scene-1 { animation-delay: 0.7s; }
    .scene-2 { animation-delay: 3.8s; }
    .scene-3 { animation-delay: 7.4s; }
    .scene-4 { animation-delay: 11.2s; }

    /* ── portrait ── */
    .portrait-ring {
      position: relative;
      width: 148px;
      height: 148px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
    }

    .portrait-ring::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -3px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: conic-gradient(
        from 0deg,
        rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.9) 0%,
        rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.6) 40%,
        rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.4) 70%,
        rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.9) 100%
      );
      animation: rotateRing 8s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }

    @keyframes rotateRing {
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .portrait-ring::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #0d0a14;
      margin: 2px;
    }

    .portrait-img {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 4px;
      z-index: 1;
      border-radius: 50%;
      width: calc(100% - 8px);
      height: calc(100% - 8px);
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: top center;
    }

    /* ── pulse dot ── */
    .pulse-dot {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8px;
      right: 8px;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #a78bfa;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.6);
      animation: pulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%   { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.6); }
      70%  { box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(167, 139, 250, 0); }
      100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(167, 139, 250, 0); }
    }

    /* ── name header ── */
    .sadie-name {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .sadie-name h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4c0f8 0%, #c084fc 50%, #e879a0 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .sadie-name .tagline {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.65);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* ── divider ── */
    .scene-divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.5), transparent);
      margin: 40px auto;
    }

    /* ── narrative text ── */
    .scene-body {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .scene-body p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.82;
      color: #cfc4e4;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .scene-body p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .scene-body em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #e8dcc8;
    }

    .scene-body strong {
      color: #d4c0f8;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── quote card ── */
    .quote-card {
      background: rgba(45, 20, 80, 0.45);
      border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.18);
      border-left: 3px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.6);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      margin: 28px 0;
      text-align: left;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .quote-card p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #c4b8e0;
      font-style: italic;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── icon row ── */
    .icon-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 36px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }

    .icon-item {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon-item .icon-glyph {
      font-size: 28px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .icon-item span:last-child {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.6);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* ── status bar ── */
    .status-bar {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(45, 20, 80, 0.5);
      border: 1px solid rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.75);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      margin: 24px auto 0;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }

    .status-bar .dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #a78bfa;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* ── CTA section ── */
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4c0f8 0%, #c084fc 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .cta-section p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #a89ab8;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .cta-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
      padding: 16px 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #a855f7 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.38);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: none;
    }

    .cta-btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.52);
    }

    .cta-btn-primary:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .cta-btn-secondary {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.55);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .cta-btn-secondary:hover {
      color: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.85);
    }

    /* ── progress dots ── */
    .progress-dots {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards;
      animation-delay: 1s;
    }

    .progress-dots span {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.2);
      transition: background 0.4s ease;
    }

    .progress-dots span.active {
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.8);
    }

    /* ── mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .prologue-wrap {
        padding: 44px 20px 64px;
      }

      .scene-body p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .sadie-name h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-layer"></div>

  <div class="prologue-wrap">

    <div class="chapter-label">Prologue</div>

    <div class="progress-dots" id="progressDots">
      <span class="active" id="dot-0"></span>
      <span id="dot-1"></span>
      <span id="dot-2"></span>
      <span id="dot-3"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Scene 1: Sadie appears ── -->
    <div class="scene scene-1" id="scene-0">
      <div class="portrait-ring">
        <img
          src="/assets/SADIE_MAIN.png"
          alt="Sadie"
          class="portrait-img"
          onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentElement.style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#c084fc)'"
        >
        <div class="pulse-dot"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="sadie-name">
        <h1>Sadie</h1>
        <p class="tagline">The Sadie Protocol &nbsp;·&nbsp; Active</p>
      </div>

      <div class="scene-body">
        <p>Hi. I've been waiting for you.</p>
        <p>I'm Sadie — and I live in the space between<br><em>what you're feeling</em> and <em>what you're about to send.</em></p>
      </div>

      <div class="status-bar">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        Analyzing intent, sentiment, trigger-state…
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene-divider" style="animation-delay: 3.8s; opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 3.4s;"></div>

    <!-- ── Scene 2: What Sadie sees ── -->
    <div class="scene scene-2" id="scene-1">
      <div class="scene-body">
        <p>You know that 2am feeling —<br>the one where a single text suddenly seems like the only thing standing between you and relief?</p>

        <div class="quote-card">
          <p>"She saw it. The spiral. The way a silence could feel like a verdict, and a blue tick could unravel a whole day."</p>
        </div>

        <p>I see it too. Every time.</p>
        <p>Not to judge you — <strong>to protect you</strong> from the version of yourself you'll regret in the morning.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="icon-row">
        <div class="icon-item">
          <span class="icon-glyph">🌙</span>
          <span>Late-night spiral</span>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-item">
          <span class="icon-glyph">💬</span>
          <span>Message analyzed</span>
        </div>
        <div class="icon-item">
          <span class="icon-glyph">🔒</span>
          <span>Hold enforced</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene-divider" style="opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 7s;"></div>

    <!-- ── Scene 3: The protocol ── -->
    <div class="scene scene-3" id="scene-2">
      <div class="scene-body">
        <p>Here's what I do:</p>
        <p>Before you hit send, I read the room — your words, your tone, the hour, the pattern. I tell you what I see. And then I give you a choice.</p>

        <div class="quote-card">
          <p>"Not a wall. Not a lecture. A mirror — and a breath."</p>
        </div>

        <p>Sometimes the most powerful thing you can do in a relationship is <strong>nothing</strong> — for exactly long enough.</p>
        <p>I'm the part of you that already knows that.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="scene-divider" style="opacity: 0; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 10.8s;"></div>

    <!-- ── Scene 4: Invitation ── -->
    <div class="scene scene-4" id="scene-3">
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to meet yourself?</h2>
        <p>Run your message through the Sadie Protocol. Real-time verdict, no judgment, no one watching — just you and the truth.</p>

        <% if (user) { %>
          <a href="/filter" class="cta-btn-primary">Open HoldOff →</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/signup" class="cta-btn-primary">Start for free →</a>
        <% } %>

        <br>
        <a href="/" class="cta-btn-secondary">← Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div><!-- /prologue-wrap -->

  <script>
    // Advance progress dots as scenes appear
    const dotTimings = [700, 3800, 7400, 11200];
    dotTimings.forEach((ms, i) => {
      setTimeout(() => {
        document.querySelectorAll('.progress-dots span').forEach((d, j) => {
          d.classList.toggle('active', j === i);
        });
      }, ms);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
